(i) and (h) and footnote 4 to the table in 40 CFR 86.129&hyph;94(a) will be October 3, 1994, unless adverse comment is
received by September 2, 1994, upon which the amendments to 40 CFR 600.006&hyph;89(b)(1) (i) and (h) and footnote
4 to the table in 40 CFR 86.129&hyph;94(a) will be withdrawn before the effective date by a document published in the

