 Comments regarding the amendments to 40 CFR 600.006&hyph;89(b)(1) (i) and (h) and footnote 4 to the table in 40 CFR
86.129&hyph;94(a) should be submitted to EPA Air Docket LE&hyph;131 (address following). Comments regarding the
information collection requirements should be sent to Chief, Information Policy Branch (PM&hyph;2136); U.S. Environmental
Protection Agency; 401 M Street, SW., Washington, DC 20460; and to the Office of Information and Regulatory Affairs,
Office of Management and Budget, Washington, DC 20503, marked ``Attention: Desk Officer for EPA.'' Materials relevant
to this final rule are contained in EPA Air Docket LE&hyph;131, Attention: Docket No. A&hyph;89&hyph;24, located
at the Air Docket Section, U.S. Environmental Protection Agency, Room M&hyph;1500, 401 M Street SW., Washington,
DC 20460 telephone (202) 382&hyph;7548. The docket may be inspected between the hours of 8:30 a.m. to 12 noon and from
1:30 to 3:30 p.m. weekdays. A reasonable fee may be charged by EPA for copying docket materials.
